        <h1 style="font-size: 25px; margin: 14px 0 0 0; line-height: 1;"><b>DopDiner</b></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="hero_sec">
        <h1>Caught Scrolling Again?</h1>
        <h2>We've got something better for your brain</h2>
       <p>Choose from our menu of mood-boosting activities designed to give you genuine satisfaction.</p>
       <p>Because life's too short for empty content.</p>
       <p>Start your dopamine menu journey today.</p>

       <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">âš¡</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <h3>5-Minute Boost</h3>
                <p>Quick dopamine activities</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">ðŸŽ¯</div>
